Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> statement
Rule 1     expression -> expression PLUS expression
Rule 2     expression -> expression MINUS expression
Rule 3     expression -> expression TIMES expression
Rule 4     expression -> expression DIVIDE expression
Rule 5     expression -> expression LT expression
Rule 6     expression -> expression GT expression
Rule 7     expression -> expression EQ expression
Rule 8     expression -> NUMBER
Rule 9     expression -> LPAREN expression RPAREN
Rule 10    statement -> expression SEMI

